skipToKey

public static void skipToKey(JsonParser parser,
                             java.lang.String keyToFind)
                      throws java.io.IOException
Skips the values of all keys in the current object until it finds the given key.

The current token will either be the JsonToken#END_OBJECT of the current object if the key is not found, or the value of the key that was found.

Parameters:
parser - JSON parser
keyToFind - key to find
Throws:
java.io.IOException - I/O exception
